column16: Contextual information on Median time to give effect to the order to act against illegal content

Discord measures the time to give effect to an order to act against illegal content from the time that it is received until the time that the submitting authority has either (a) provided a complete and valid order  or request, or (b) withdraws the order or request. The longer median times reported are due to follow up or additional communication to obtain the information necessary to give effect to the order or request.
